{"date":"1945-07-07","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/57/3e/262704_c0MNm.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/57/3e/262704_c0MNm.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/57/3e/262704_c0MNm.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/57/3e/262704_c0MNm.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/57/3e/262704_c0MNm.jpg"},"summary":"　　夜深人静，温暖的乡间小屋。汤姆安然地窝在墙角熟睡，而小老鼠杰瑞却在奋笔疾书。他似乎厌倦了乡村无聊的生活，于是写信告诉汤姆，自己要去大城市闯荡，开拓视野。随着咣咣作响的火车，杰瑞来到了曼哈顿。帝国大厦的雄伟以及车水马龙的喧嚣都令他兴奋不已。他时而和玩具娃娃翩翩起舞，时而又搭乘着小舟和站街流莺打着轻薄的呼哨。 \r\n　　一切似乎完美，可是大城市有大城市的烦恼，杰瑞受到来往汽车的追逐险些送命，更在夜晚见到了城市角落里黑暗恐怖的一幕。一次意外，让他成为珠宝大盗遭到警察的追捕，黑暗向他袭来，他也许该回想一下家的温暖了……","name":"Mouse in Manhattan","name_cn":"老鼠在曼哈顿","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":32,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":19,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1945","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"猫和老鼠","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"米高梅","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1940-1949","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1940s","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"8(+3)","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Short_film","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"泡面番","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Short","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"MGM","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"老鼠在曼哈顿"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1945-07-07"},{"key":"片长","value":"7分53秒"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"}],"rating":{"rank":712,"total":70,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":3,"7":18,"8":30,"9":13,"10":5},"score":7.9},"total_episodes":1,"collection":{"on_hold":2,"dropped":8,"wish":14,"collect":138,"doing":1},"id":262704,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["剧场版","欧美"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2}